item.title: Final Project Ideas
item.description: Week 1 I am still not 100% certain what I would like to pursue for the final project, so I am going to list several ideas that I am considering. I hope to chat with someone on the course staff to consult on the feasibility of each idea before making a final decision. Idea 1: Farming Robot This was something I mentioned in the application for this class, but I think it might be beyond the realm of possibility.
